								[| {|get_CLID_Wait,Wait::entered,terminate|} |]
								dbisim(Clock_CLID_Wait(id__,0,
										          const_RandomWalk_lv,
										          const_RandomWalk_av,
										          const_RandomWalk_pi,
										          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef))
							)\{|get_CLID_Wait|}
						)
						) \ diff(union(stateClockSync,enteredSS),enteredSS)
					)
					)
				
				Stateful_VS_O(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = 
					dbisim((let
						getsetLocalChannels = {|get_randcoef,set_randcoef,
						get_sign,set_sign,
						get_rwCmd,set_rwCmd|}
						clockSync = {|get_CLID_T,clockReset.CLID_T|}
					within
						(Behaviour_VS_O(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
								    const_RandomWalk_lv,
								    const_RandomWalk_av,
								    const_RandomWalk_pi,
								    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) 
						 [| union(union(getsetLocalChannels,clockSync),{terminate}) |] 
						 (varMemory(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						 		    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						 		    const_RandomWalk_av,
						 		    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						 		    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) [| {terminate} |] Clocks(id__,
						 		          const_RandomWalk_lv,
						 		          const_RandomWalk_av,
						 		          const_RandomWalk_pi,
						 		          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef))
					 	)\union(getsetLocalChannels,clockSync)
					)
					)
				
				IteratedStateful_VS_O(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) =
					(dbisim(
						sbisim(
							dbisim(
								sbisim(
									dbisim(
										sbisim(
											dbisim(
												sbisim(
													IteratedBehaviour_VS_O(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
															    const_RandomWalk_lv,
															    const_RandomWalk_av,
															    const_RandomWalk_pi,
															    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef)
													[| {|get_CLID_T,clockReset.CLID_T,terminate|} |]
													dbisim(Clock_CLID_T(id__,0,
															          const_RandomWalk_lv,
															          const_RandomWalk_av,
															          const_RandomWalk_pi,
															          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef))
												)\{|get_CLID_T,clockReset.CLID_T|}
											)
											[| {|get_rwCmd,set_rwCmd,terminate|} |]
											Memory_rwCmd((0,0))
										)\{|get_rwCmd,set_rwCmd|}
									)
									[| {|get_sign,set_sign,terminate|} |]
									Memory_sign(1)
								)\{|get_sign,set_sign|}
							)
							[| {|get_randcoef,set_randcoef,terminate|} |]
							Memory_randcoef(const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef)
						)\{|get_randcoef,set_randcoef|}
					)
					)
				
				-- END
				
				-- Memory
				-- Memory variables
				Memory_randcoef(randcoef) =
					get_randcoef!randcoef -> Memory_randcoef(randcoef)
					[]
					set_randcoef?x__ -> Memory_randcoef(x__)
					[]
					terminate -> SKIP
				Memory_sign(sign) =
					get_sign!sign -> Memory_sign(sign)
					[]
					set_sign?x__ -> Memory_sign(x__)
					[]
					terminate -> SKIP
				Memory_rwCmd(rwCmd) =
					get_rwCmd!rwCmd -> Memory_rwCmd(rwCmd)
					[]
					set_rwCmd?x__ -> Memory_rwCmd(x__)
					[]
					terminate -> SKIP
				
				-- varMemory process
				varMemory(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = Memory_randcoef(const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef)
				[| { terminate } |] (
				Memory_sign(1)
				[| { terminate } |] (
				Memory_rwCmd((0,0))
				)
				)
				
				getsetLocalChannels = {|get_randcoef,set_randcoef,get_sign,set_sign,get_rwCmd,set_rwCmd|}
				
				-- Definition of the behaviour of state machines (default, optimised, visible, visible and optimised)
				FVS__(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = STM_VS_O(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) \ localClockResets
				D__(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = timed_priority(STM(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) \ union(internal_events,localClockResets))
				O__(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = dbisim(D__(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef))
				VS__(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = FVS__(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef)
				VS_O__(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = dbisim(FVS__(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef))
				HEXT__(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = O__(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) [|shared_variable_events|] SKIP
				FVS_C__(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = dbisim(timed_priority(STM(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) \ internal_events))
				HUP__(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = timed_priority(O__(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) [|{share__}|] SKIP)
				
				-- Clocks
				Clock_CLID_T(id__,x__,
						          const_RandomWalk_lv,
						          const_RandomWalk_av,
						          const_RandomWalk_pi,
						          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = 
					TimeOut_1(
						clockReset.CLID_T -> Clock_CLID_T(id__,0,
								          const_RandomWalk_lv,
								          const_RandomWalk_av,
								          const_RandomWalk_pi,
								          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef)
						[]
						get_CLID_T!x__ -> Clock_CLID_T(id__,x__,
								          const_RandomWalk_lv,
								          const_RandomWalk_av,
								          const_RandomWalk_pi,
								          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef)
						[]
						terminate -> SKIP,Clock_CLID_T(id__,clock_type_plus(x__,1,CLID_T_clock_type(id__,
								          const_RandomWalk_lv,
								          const_RandomWalk_av,
								          const_RandomWalk_pi,
								          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef)),
								          const_RandomWalk_lv,
								          const_RandomWalk_av,
								          const_RandomWalk_pi,
								          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef))
				
				Clocks(id__,
						          const_RandomWalk_lv,
						          const_RandomWalk_av,
						          const_RandomWalk_pi,
						          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = dbisim(Clock_CLID_T(id__,0,
						          const_RandomWalk_lv,
						          const_RandomWalk_av,
						          const_RandomWalk_pi,
						          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef))
				
				clockSync = {|get_CLID_T,clockReset.CLID_T|}
				
				Clock_CLID_Wait(id__,x__,
						          const_RandomWalk_lv,
						          const_RandomWalk_av,
						          const_RandomWalk_pi,
						          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = 
					TimeOut_1(
						Wait::entered -> Clock_CLID_Wait(id__,0,
								          const_RandomWalk_lv,
								          const_RandomWalk_av,
								          const_RandomWalk_pi,
								          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef)
						[]
						get_CLID_Wait!x__ -> Clock_CLID_Wait(id__,x__,
								          const_RandomWalk_lv,
								          const_RandomWalk_av,
								          const_RandomWalk_pi,
								          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef)
						[]
						terminate -> SKIP,Clock_CLID_Wait(id__,clock_type_plus(x__,1,CLID_Wait_clock_type(id__,
								          const_RandomWalk_lv,
								          const_RandomWalk_av,
								          const_RandomWalk_pi,
								          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef)),
								          const_RandomWalk_lv,
								          const_RandomWalk_av,
								          const_RandomWalk_pi,
								          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef))
				Clock_CLID_Wander(id__,x__,
						          const_RandomWalk_lv,
						          const_RandomWalk_av,
						          const_RandomWalk_pi,
						          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = 
					TimeOut_1(
						Wander::entered -> Clock_CLID_Wander(id__,0,
								          const_RandomWalk_lv,
								          const_RandomWalk_av,
								          const_RandomWalk_pi,
								          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef)
						[]
						get_CLID_Wander!x__ -> Clock_CLID_Wander(id__,x__,
								          const_RandomWalk_lv,
								          const_RandomWalk_av,
								          const_RandomWalk_pi,
								          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef)
						[]
						terminate -> SKIP,Clock_CLID_Wander(id__,clock_type_plus(x__,1,CLID_Wander_clock_type(id__,
								          const_RandomWalk_lv,
								          const_RandomWalk_av,
								          const_RandomWalk_pi,
								          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef)),
								          const_RandomWalk_lv,
								          const_RandomWalk_av,
								          const_RandomWalk_pi,
								          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef))
				
				StateClocks(id__,
						          const_RandomWalk_lv,
						          const_RandomWalk_av,
						          const_RandomWalk_pi,
						          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = dbisim(Clock_CLID_Wait(id__,0,
						          const_RandomWalk_lv,
						          const_RandomWalk_av,
						          const_RandomWalk_pi,
						          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef))
				[| { terminate } |] (
				dbisim(Clock_CLID_Wander(id__,0,
						          const_RandomWalk_lv,
						          const_RandomWalk_av,
						          const_RandomWalk_pi,
						          const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef))
				)
				
				stateClockSync = {|get_CLID_Wait,Wait::entered,get_CLID_Wander,Wander::entered|}
				
				
				-- Shared memory
				-- Shared memory variables
				
				Memory_EnableClusterWatch(x__) = (
					get_EnableClusterWatch!x__ -> Memory_EnableClusterWatch(x__)
					[]
					registerRead.i_EnableClusterWatch?x__ -> Memory_EnableClusterWatch(x__)
					[]
					terminate -> SKIP
				)
				Memory_DisableClusterWatch(x__) = (
					get_DisableClusterWatch!x__ -> Memory_DisableClusterWatch(x__)
					[]
					registerRead.i_DisableClusterWatch?x__ -> Memory_DisableClusterWatch(x__)
					[]
					terminate -> SKIP
				)
				
				-- sharedVarMemory process
				sharedVarMemory(id__,cycle_RandomWalk_RandomWalk,
						    const_RandomWalk_lv,
						    const_RandomWalk_av,
						    const_RandomWalk_pi,
						    const_RandomWalk_v_randcoef) = (
				 (terminate -> SKIP
				 )
				 [| { terminate } |]
				 (Memory_EnableClusterWatch(false)
				 [| { terminate } |] (
				 Memory_DisableClusterWatch(false)
				 )
				 )
				)
				
				sharedVarSync = union({|get_EnableClusterWatch,
				get_DisableClusterWatch|},
					  {||}
					 )
				
				sharedVarHide = union({|get_EnableClusterWatch,
				get_DisableClusterWatch|},
					  {||}
					 )
				
				}
		endmodule
		module stm_ref4
		exports
			transparent diamond
			transparent sbisim
			transparent dbisim
			transparent chase
		
			-- Transition identifiers
			-- declaring identifiers of transitions
			datatype NIDS = 
			              NID_i0|
			              NID_DetectingTarget|
			              NID_WaitingForTarget
			
			channel internal__ : NIDS
			
			-- Flow channels		
			channel interrupt
			channel exited
			channel exit
			channel terminate
			
			-- Variable channels
			channel get_targetObjectxy, set_targetObjectxy, setL_targetObjectxy, setR_targetObjectxy: Vec2
			channel get_closestTargetObject, set_closestTargetObject, setL_closestTargetObject, setR_closestTargetObject: ObjectData
			channel get_closestTargetObjectPosition, set_closestTargetObjectPosition, setL_closestTargetObjectPosition, setR_closestTargetObjectPosition: Vec2
			channel get_counter, set_counter, setL_counter, setR_counter: core_nat
			channel get_data, set_data, setL_data, setR_data: {(x0__,x1__,x2__) | x0__ <- core_nat,x1__ <- LSeq(ClusterData,2),x2__ <- LSeq(ObjectData,2)}
			channel get_done, set_done, setL_done, setR_done: core_boolean
			channel get_validObject, set_validObject, setL_validObject, setR_validObject: core_boolean
			channel get_targetType, set_targetType, setL_targetType, setR_targetType: core_nat
			channel get_m, set_m, setL_m, setR_m: LSeq(ClusterData,2)
			
			-- Shared variable channels
			
			-- Local variable channels for defined operations that are required by the state machine
			
			-- Declaring state machine events
			
			-- Declaring call and ret events for undefined operations
			
			enterSS = {|
			i0::enter,
			DetectingTarget::enter,
			WaitingForTarget::enter
			|}
			
			enteredSS = 	{|
			DetectingTarget::entered,
			WaitingForTarget::entered
			|}
			
			internal_events = union(enteredSS,union(enterSS,{|interrupt,exited|}))
			
			shared_variable_events = {|
			|}
			
			
			channel clockReset, clockResetL, clockResetR 
			
			localClockResets = {||}
			
			
			channel get_CLID_WaitingForTarget : core_clock_type 
			channel get_CLID_DetectingTarget : core_clock_type 
			--channel increment__
			
			CLID_WaitingForTarget_clock_type(id__,
					          const_TargetWatch_ObjectThreshold) = 
				let
					max = (clock_type_max(Union({
			{}
			}))+1)
				ctype = {0..max}
			within
				if member(max,core_clock_type) then ctype else error("core_clock_type is not wide enough")
			
			CLID_DetectingTarget_clock_type(id__,
					          const_TargetWatch_ObjectThreshold) = 
				let
					max = (clock_type_max(Union({
			{}
			}))+1)
				ctype = {0..max}
			within
				if member(max,core_clock_type) then ctype else error("core_clock_type is not wide enough")
			
			
			
			-- RoboSim-specific declarations
			channel endexec, endexec_action
			channel endexec__ : NIDS
			channel startexec, startexec_action
			
			-- declaring registerRead/Write datatypes
			datatype RegisterDataInput = i_EnableTargetWatch.Bool.Vec2
				| i_VisibleClustersTW.Bool.{(x0__,x1__,x2__) | x0__ <- core_nat,x1__ <- LSeq(ClusterData,2),x2__ <- LSeq(ObjectData,2)}
				| i_DisableTargetWatch.Bool
				| i_CurrentTypeTW.Bool.core_nat
				| i_CachePointsTW.Bool.LSeq(ClusterData,2)
			
			
			datatype RegisterDataOutput = o_TargetObject.Vec2
				| o_InvalidTarget
			
			
			nametype RegisterOutputs = {|
			o_TargetObject,
			o_InvalidTarget|}
				
			nametype RegisterInputs = {|
			i_EnableTargetWatch,
			i_VisibleClustersTW,
			i_DisableTargetWatch,
			i_CurrentTypeTW,
			i_CachePointsTW|}
			
			channel registerRead 	: RegisterDataInput
			channel registerWrite 	: RegisterDataOutput
			
			-- variable channels
			channel get_EnableTargetWatch : Bool.Vec2
			channel get_DisableTargetWatch : Bool
			channel get_VisibleClustersTW : Bool.{(x0__,x1__,x2__) | x0__ <- core_nat,x1__ <- LSeq(ClusterData,2),x2__ <- LSeq(ObjectData,2)}
			channel get_CurrentTypeTW : Bool.core_nat
			channel get_CachePointsTW : Bool.LSeq(ClusterData,2)
			
			-- channel set with all visible events
			sem__events = {|endexec,terminate
						,registerRead
						,registerWrite
				|}
		
				-- Nodes --
				-- declaring all nodes
				
				----------------------------------------------------------------------
				-- Initial: i0
				module i0
				exports
				
					channel enter, interrupt
					
					Timed(OneStep) {
						D__(id__,cycle_TargetWatch_TargetWatch,
								    const_TargetWatch_ObjectThreshold) = 
							dbisim(let
								Inactive 	= share__choice(enter -> SKIP [] terminate -> SKIP) ; Active
								
								Termination = terminate -> SKIP
								
								Active 		= share__choice(interrupt -> SKIP) ; Inactive
							within
								Inactive [| {terminate} |> SKIP)
						
						VS_O__(id__,cycle_TargetWatch_TargetWatch,
								    const_TargetWatch_ObjectThreshold) = D__(id__,cycle_TargetWatch_TargetWatch,
								    const_TargetWatch_ObjectThreshold)
					}
				
				endmodule
				----------------------------------------------------------------------
				
				
				----------------------------------------------------------------------
				-- State: DetectingTarget
				module DetectingTarget
				
				enterSS = 
						{|			ValidateTargetObject::enter,
							PublishTargetObject::enter,
							CalculateTargetObject::enter,
							i0::enter,
							WaitForDisableTargetWatch::enter
						|}
				enteredSS = 
						{|			ValidateTargetObject::entered,
							PublishTargetObject::entered,
							CalculateTargetObject::entered,
							WaitForDisableTargetWatch::entered
						|}
				exports
				
					--  Declarations
					channel endexec__ : NIDS
					
					
					channel enter, entered, interrupt
					channel enteredL, enteredR
					
									
					-- declaring identifiers of transitions
					datatype NIDS = 
					              NID_ValidateTargetObject|
					              NID_PublishTargetObject|
					              NID_CalculateTargetObject|
					              NID_i0|
					              NID_WaitForDisableTargetWatch
					
					channel internal__ : NIDS
					
					channel get_CLID_WaitForDisableTargetWatch : core_clock_type 
					channel get_CLID_PublishTargetObject : core_clock_type 
					channel get_CLID_ValidateTargetObject : core_clock_type 
					channel get_CLID_CalculateTargetObject : core_clock_type 
					--channel increment__
					
					CLID_WaitForDisableTargetWatch_clock_type(id__,
							          const_TargetWatch_ObjectThreshold) = 
						let
							max = (clock_type_max(Union({
					{}
					}))+1)
						ctype = {0..max}
					within
						if member(max,core_clock_type) then ctype else error("core_clock_type is not wide enough")
					
					CLID_PublishTargetObject_clock_type(id__,
							          const_TargetWatch_ObjectThreshold) = 
						let
							max = (clock_type_max(Union({
					{}
					}))+1)
						ctype = {0..max}
					within
						if member(max,core_clock_type) then ctype else error("core_clock_type is not wide enough")
					
					CLID_ValidateTargetObject_clock_type(id__,
							          const_TargetWatch_ObjectThreshold) = 
						let
							max = (clock_type_max(Union({
					{}
					}))+1)
						ctype = {0..max}
					within
						if member(max,core_clock_type) then ctype else error("core_clock_type is not wide enough")
					
					CLID_CalculateTargetObject_clock_type(id__,
							          const_TargetWatch_ObjectThreshold) = 
						let
							max = (clock_type_max(Union({
					{}
					}))+1)
						ctype = {0..max}
					within
						if member(max,core_clock_type) then ctype else error("core_clock_type is not wide enough")
					
					
					--	Nodes
					-- declaring all nodes
					
					----------------------------------------------------------------------
					-- State: ValidateTargetObject
					module ValidateTargetObject
					
					enterSS = {}
					
					enteredSS = {}
					
					exports
					
						--  Declarations
						channel endexec__ : NIDS
						
						
						channel enter, entered, interrupt
						channel enteredL, enteredR
						
										
						
						--channel increment__
						
						
						--	Nodes
						-- declaring all nodes
						
						
						Timed(OneStep) {
							--	Rule: behaviours(Node)
							--  Note that FDR has problems with efficiently compiling the process below
							-- 	if using a different recursion pattern.
							D__(id__,cycle_TargetWatch_TargetWatch,
									    const_TargetWatch_ObjectThreshold) = 
							dbisim(let
								-- IMPLEMENTATION NOTE: 
								-- The following should be defined as: Inactive = share__choice(Activation [] Termination),
								-- however FDR struggles with that form in certain cases. So we use the exception operator
								-- instead to 'terminate'.
								
								Inactive 	= share__choice(enter -> SKIP [] terminate -> SKIP) ; Active
								
								Termination = terminate -> SKIP
								
								Active 		= share__choice(get_closestTargetObject?closestTargetObject -> share__choice(get_m?m -> share__choice(get_targetObjectxy?targetObjectxy -> share__choice(get_targetType?targetType -> true&(if (((ObjectData_clusterID(closestTargetObject)==ClusterData_clusterID(access_(m, targetType)))) or ((distance(ObjectData_position(closestTargetObject),targetObjectxy)<const_TargetWatch_ObjectThreshold))) then (share__choice(true & (share__choice(set_validObject!false -> SKIP))))else SKIP))))) ; 
										 	  Behaviour ; 
										 	  share__choice(exit -> SKIP) ; SKIP ; 
										 	  share__choice(exited -> SKIP) ; Inactive
							
								Behaviour 	= entered -> During
								During 		= ((SKIP ; SStop) /\ interrupt -> SKIP)
							within
								Inactive [| {terminate} |> SKIP)
								
							VS_O__(id__,cycle_TargetWatch_TargetWatch,
									    const_TargetWatch_ObjectThreshold) = 
							dbisim(let
								Inactive 	= share__choice(enter -> SKIP [] terminate -> SKIP) ; Active
								
								Termination = terminate -> SKIP
								
								Active 		= share__choice(get_closestTargetObject?closestTargetObject -> share__choice(get_m?m -> share__choice(get_targetObjectxy?targetObjectxy -> share__choice(get_targetType?targetType -> true&(if (((ObjectData_clusterID(closestTargetObject)==ClusterData_clusterID(access_(m, targetType)))) or ((distance(ObjectData_position(closestTargetObject),targetObjectxy)<const_TargetWatch_ObjectThreshold))) then (share__choice(true & (share__choice(set_validObject!false -> SKIP))))else SKIP))))) ; 
										 	  Behaviour ; 
										 	  share__choice(exit -> SKIP) ; SKIP ; 
										 	  share__choice(exited -> SKIP) ; Inactive
							
								Behaviour 	= entered -> During
								During 		= ((SKIP ; SStop) /\ interrupt -> SKIP)
							within
								Inactive [| {terminate} |> SKIP)
							
							
							-- Clocks
							
							StateClocks(id__,
									          const_TargetWatch_ObjectThreshold) = terminate -> SKIP
							
							stateClockSync = {||}
						}
					
					endmodule
					----------------------------------------------------------------------
					
					
					----------------------------------------------------------------------
					-- State: PublishTargetObject
					module PublishTargetObject
					
					enterSS = {}
					
					enteredSS = {}
					
					exports
					
